                                    oc:textContent "**Retry timing best practices:**" ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 5 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**Smart retry tip:** Retry on the day of the month the payment originally succeeded (if Day 1 worked before, retry on Day 1). Stripe Smart Retries handles this automatically." ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "Not all failures are the same. Retry strategy by decline type:" ],
                                [ a oc:Table ;
                                    oc:blockType "table" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                    oc:rowCount 3 ;
                                    oc:tableCaption "Not all failures are the same. Retry strategy by decline type" ;
                                    oc:tableMarkdown """| Decline Type | Examples | Retry Strategy |
|-------------|----------|----------------|
| Soft decline (temporary) | Insufficient funds, processor timeout | Retry 3-5 times over 7-10 days |
| Hard decline (permanent) | Card stolen, account closed | Don't retry — ask for new card |
| Authentication required | 3D Secure, SCA | Send customer to update payment |
""" ],
