                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "Track these leading indicators of churn:" ],
                                [ a oc:Table ;
                                    oc:blockType "table" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                    oc:rowCount 8 ;
                                    oc:tableCaption "Track these leading indicators of churn" ;
                                    oc:tableMarkdown """| Signal | Risk Level | Timeframe |
|--------|-----------|-----------|
| Login frequency drops 50%+ | High | 2-4 weeks before cancel |
| Key feature usage stops | High | 1-3 weeks before cancel |
| Support tickets spike then stop | High | 1-2 weeks before cancel |
| Email open rates decline | Medium | 2-6 weeks before cancel |
| Billing page visits increase | High | Days before cancel |
| Team seats removed | High | 1-2 weeks before cancel |
| Data export initiated | Critical | Days before cancel |
| NPS score drops below 6 | Medium | 1-3 months before cancel |
""" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 15 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Risk Signals" ],
                        [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:Table ;
                                    oc:blockType "table" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                                    oc:rowCount 6 ;
                                    oc:tableCaption "**Before they think about cancelling:**" ;
                                    oc:tableMarkdown """| Trigger | Intervention |
|---------|-------------|
| Usage drop >50% for 2 weeks | "We noticed you haven't used [feature]. Need help?" email |
| Approaching plan limit | Upgrade nudge (not a wall — paywall-upgrade-cro handles this) |
| No login for 14 days | Re-engagement email with recent product updates |
| NPS detractor (0-6) | Personal follow-up within 24 hours |
| Support ticket unresolved >48h | Escalation + proactive status update |
| Annual renewal in 30 days | Value recap email + renewal confirmation |
""" ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "**Before they think about cancelling:**" ] ;
                            oc:sectionLevel 3 ;
                            oc:sectionOrder 17 ;
                            oc:sectionTitle "Proactive Interventions" ],
                        [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:Table ;
                                    oc:blockType "table" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                                    oc:rowCount 4 ;
                                    oc:tableCaption "```" ;
                                    oc:tableMarkdown """| Score | Status | Action |
|-------|--------|--------|
| 80-100 | Healthy | Upsell opportunities |
| 60-79 | Needs attention | Proactive check-in |
| 40-59 | At risk | Intervention campaign |
| 0-39 | Critical | Personal outreach |
""" ],
                                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "Build a simple health score (0-100) from weighted signals:" ],
                                [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """Health Score = (
  Login frequency score × 0.30 +
